<plot>'Picturesque Joel' is a static-posed, visual representation of a day in a young man's life as he plans a romantic evening with a blind date. The essential picture moments are recorded live action with some stop motion techniques. It is meant to give a quality of directness to the action within the story. These important picture-moments are what are to be best remembered.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?432114</url></doc>
